. *============================================================================
> ===
. * prepare_data.do — Prepare analysis datasets
. *
. * Analog of DGM prepare_datasets.do:
. *   DGM: merge FICUS-FARE with EAP price data, generate s/v/k/m/o
. *   Us:  load rebuilt data, generate analysis variables, winsorize
