. dis _newline "--- prepare_data.do ---"

--- prepare_data.do ---

. 
. use "$srcdata", clear

. xtset id year, yearly

Panel variable: id (unbalanced)
 Time variable: year, 2006 to 2021, but with gaps
         Delta: 1 year

. 
. dis "Source data: " _N " obs, " year[1] "-" year[_N]
Source data: 9164 obs, 2006-2021

