. * 1c. Calculate firm-level markups
. do "$datagen/calculate_markups.do"

. *============================================================================
> ===
. * calculate_markups.do — Compute firm-level markups from PF coefficients
. *
. * Analog of DGM markup_calculation.do:
. *   DGM: elasticity × (sales/materials), 4 specs × 10 treatments
. *   Us:  θ/α for CD and TL, 6 specs (A-E + OLS)
. *
. * Markup formula (DLW 2012):
. *   CD:  μ = β_cogs / α,  where α = exp(cogs)/exp(y_c)
. *   TL:  μ = (β_cogs + 2·β_cogs2·cogs + β_kcogs·k) / α
. *
. * Input:  analysisdata/analysis_panel.dta + coefficients_byind.dta
. * Output: analysisdata/markups_panel.dta
. *============================================================================
> ===
. 
. dis _newline "--- calculate_markups.do ---"

--- calculate_markups.do ---

. 
. use "$data/analysis_panel.dta", clear

. xtset id year, yearly

Panel variable: id (unbalanced)
 Time variable: year, 2006 to 2021, but with gaps
         Delta: 1 year

. 
. * Load coefficients
. preserve

. use "$data/coefficients_byind.dta", clear

. tempfile coeff

. save `coeff'
file /var/folders/4c/ww4k0h5j0fq1529s2dttb4t00000gn/T//St29358.000002 saved
    as .dta format

. restore

. 
. * Merge coefficients by nace2
. merge m:1 nace2 using `coeff', assert(3) nogen
(variable nace2 was byte, now float to accommodate using data's values)

    Result                      Number of obs
    -----------------------------------------
    Not matched                             0
    Matched                             9,164  
    -----------------------------------------

. 
. *-----------------------------------------------------------------------
. * First stage (needed for corrected α)
. *-----------------------------------------------------------------------
. 
. * We need phi and epsilon. Re-run first stage by industry.
. gen phi = .
(9,164 missing values generated)

. gen epsilon = .
(9,164 missing values generated)

. 
. levelsof nace2, local(naces)
41 42 43

. foreach n of local naces {
  2.     xi: qui reg go c.k*#pp_dummy c.cogs*#pp_dummy i.year if nace2 == `n'
  3.     predict phi_`n' if nace2 == `n'
  4.     predict eps_`n' if nace2 == `n', res
  5.     replace phi = phi_`n' if nace2 == `n'
  6.     replace epsilon = eps_`n' if nace2 == `n'
  7.     drop phi_`n' eps_`n' _I*
  8. }
i.year            _Iyear_2006-2021    (naturally coded; _Iyear_2006 omitted)
